- `motor>=3.3.2`
- `beanie>=1.23.6`
- `redis>=6.4.0`

### Email
- `emails>=0.6`
- `jinja2>=3.1.6`

### Monitoring
- `prometheus-client>=0.19.0`
- `structlog>=23.2.0`

## ğŸ› ï¸ Development

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone <repo-url>
cd quant-pack

# Install with development dependencies
pip install -e .[full,dev]

# Run tests
pytest

# Format code
black src/
ruff check src/ --fix

# Type checking
mypy src/mysingle/
```

